longDescription:
The Adult Dog Wellness Plan Includes:
  • 2 Complete Physical Exams
  • Core Vaccination Series as Recommended by Your Veterinarian - May Include 5-in-1 (DAP/Parvo), Lepto 4, Bordetella and Rabies
  • Fecal Test
  • Deworming Treatment - Roundworms and Hookworms
  • Heartworm/Lyme Combo Test
  • Vet Screen and CBC
Optional Services Include:
  • Microchip I.D. and Registration
